        {
            "title": "北角酒吧酒客疑「爭咪」 雙方互毀釀3傷 警拘捕兩男女",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"其中一名女傷者手部受傷，由救護車送院治理。黎志偉攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/83d3ff1a3c396c8aaefa724515636cc5/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250419/_2025041904363444875.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">其中一名女傷者手部受傷，由救護車送院治理。黎志偉攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>北角發生打鬥案。今日（19日）凌晨1時許，警方接獲報案，指北角英皇道58-60一間酒吧內有人打鬥。警方接報到場，經初步調查，拘捕其中 一男一女涉嫌「在公眾地方打鬥」。\n\n</p>\n<p>消息指，酒吧內兩名女子一直霸著唱K，令其他在場人士未能唱歌，一名酒客對此感不滿，遂上前與兩女發生口角，雙方繼而動武。事件中，一名男子眼角受傷；另外兩名女傷者則頭及手受傷。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4203494/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一名女傷者頭部受傷送院。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6fca11dd91a5176c54a3a2bcd9102424/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-19-03-54-34_003.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一名女傷者頭部受傷送院。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4203495/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方拘捕一男一女，涉涉嫌「在公眾地方打鬥」。黎志偉攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/26dac3f9ababef52bd7415ff22dacf1a/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-19-03-55-10_009.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方拘捕一男一女，涉涉嫌「在公眾地方打鬥」。黎志偉攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064690/即時-港聞-北角酒吧酒客疑-爭咪-雙方互毀釀3傷-警拘捕兩男女",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-19 04:45:59",
