            "title": "北大嶼山公路有人暈倒路邊 親友揮手截車 熱心司機停車協助",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"北大嶼山公路有人暈倒路邊，親友揮手截車，熱心司機停車協助。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/8bba32813c16bd83f43207898c0463a8/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250419/_2025041901164219015.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">北大嶼山公路有人暈倒路邊，親友揮手截車，熱心司機停車協助。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>北大嶼山發生有人暈倒事件。網上平台流傳一段片段，指下午約1時，有外籍人士在北大嶼山公路路邊暈倒，事主「屋企人求救好無助」。\n\n</p>\n<p>由網上一段車Cam片段可見，拍攝的車輛當時沿北大嶼山公路住九龍方向行駛，途至映灣園對開時，約5名人士在公路路肩位置，其中一人懷疑身體不適坐在地上，另外有兩名非華裔男子在路邊揮手，示意途經車輛停下協助。帖主見狀後，立即將車駛至路肩停車，兩名非華裔男子立即上前，疑向片主講述事件並尋求協助。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4203441/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"兩名非華裔男子尋求協助。Facebook群組 車Cam L 片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/99ddedd0ae3e657a9290072674f26c85/2025-04/2025-04-19_00_55_07.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        兩名非華裔男子尋求協助。Facebook群組 車Cam L 片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4203442/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"兩名非華裔男子尋求協助。Facebook群組 車Cam L 片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1656eb50a00845391a9b31ba621f8994/2025-04/2025-04-19_00_55_26.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        兩名非華裔男子尋求協助。Facebook群組 車Cam L 片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4203443/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"兩名非華裔男子尋求協助。Facebook群組 車Cam L 片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/60592df42b93f30d01a96ce2fea99f46/2025-04/2025-04-19_00_55_30.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        兩名非華裔男子尋求協助。Facebook群組 車Cam L 片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4203444/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"穿紅衣服男子上前協助。Facebook群組 車Cam L 片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/42c5ab284172935413b880faf8ae4abe/2025-04/2025-04-19_00_55_40.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        穿紅衣服男子上前協助。Facebook群組 車Cam L 片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4203445/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"穿紅衣服男子上前協助。Facebook群組 車Cam L 片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3483199412c15afd02353efc96f0651b/2025-04/2025-04-19_00_55_43.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        穿紅衣服男子上前協助。Facebook群組 車Cam L 片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4203446/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"穿紅衣服男子上前協助。Facebook群組 車Cam L 片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/004ae357e493754da348bdf55c1ab0c8/2025-04/2025-04-19_00_56_00.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        穿紅衣服男子上前協助。Facebook群組 車Cam L 片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>未幾，片主將車停好後，一名身穿紅色物流公司制服的男子，立即走向事主了解，影片隨即結束。據原帖透露，當時見到事主及其他人身上均有巴士公司的貼紙，希望巴士公司「注意一下」。\n\n</p>\n<p>警方表示，周五（18日）下午1時04分接獲一名輕型貨車司機報案，指在北大嶼山公路往九龍方向，近東涌牽引變電站對開，發現一名男子眩暈，遂停車協助。 另外，警方接獲另一名報案人稱，發現上址有一名非華裔女子不適。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
